'''Ahmed Ali Al-Kassar''' ([[Arabic]]:أحمد علي الكسار) is a Saudi Arabian [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for Saudi Arabian club [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]] and the [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia national team]].<ref>{{soccerway|ahmed-kassar/143650}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Al-Raed===
On 19 June 2009, [[Al-Raed FC|Al-Raed]] signed with Ahmed Al-Kassar from [[Al-Taraji Club|Al-Taraji]] for 1.8 million Saudi Riyals.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.al-jazirah.com/2009/20090601/sp38.htm|title=الرائد يوقع مع ثنائي الترجي الراهب والكسار|website=www.al-jazirah.com|accessdate=26 April 2023}}</ref> He left in 2015 to go to [[Ettifaq FC|Al-Ettifaq]].

===Al-Ettifaq===
On 10 September 2015, [[Ettifaq FC|Al-Ettifaq]] signed with Ahmed from Al-Raed.<ref>{{cite news |title=الكسار يوقع لنادي الاتفاق بنحو 17 مليون ريال |url=http://www.alriyadh.com/1081092 |access-date=26 April 2023 |work=[[Al Riyadh (newspaper)|Al Riyadh]] |date=10 September 2015 |language=ar}}</ref> He won the [[Saudi First Division]] in his first season. On 18 August 2017, Ahmed Al-Kassar made a last-minute assist for [[Hazaa Al-Hazaa]] to help [[Ettifaq FC|Al-Ettifaq]] draw 2–2 against [[Al-Nassr FC|Al-Nassr]].<ref>[http://www.albiladdaily.com/بمساعدة-الكسار-الاتفاق-يمنع-النصر-من/ بمساعدة-الكسار-الاتفاق-يمنع-النصر-من] ''[[Al-Bilad (Saudi newspaper)|Al Bilad]]'' {{Dead link|date=June 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> He became only the fifth goalkeeper to make an assist in the [[Saudi Professional League]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.kooora.com/?n=615114&o=n3055889|title = كووورة: الموقع العربي الرياضي الأول| date=9 July 2019 }}</ref> After the match, he said that manager [[Miodrag Ješić]] did not want him to go forward, but he ignored that and made the assist.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.kooora.com/?n=615080&o=n3055889|title = كووورة: الموقع العربي الرياضي الأول| date=9 July 2019 }}</ref>

===Al-Fayha===
On 20 June 2023, Al-Kassar joined [[Al-Fayha FC|Al-Fayha]] on a free transfer.<ref>{{cite web |title=الكسار ينضم للفيحاء حتى 2026 | date=20 June 2023 |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1249207}}</ref>

===Al-Qadsiah===
On 30 January 2024, Al-Kassar joined [[Al-Qadsiah FC|Al-Qadsiah]] on a three-and-a-half-year deal.<ref>{{cite web |title=الكسار يحمي عرين القادسية |url=https://www.alriyadh.com/2057053}}</ref>

